content.rendered:
Directed by Balwinder Singh Janjua. Rupinder Chahal. Jimmy Singh.

Written by Rupinder Chahal. Balwinder Singh Janjua. Anil Rodhan. Jimmy Singh.

Cast Abhishant Rana( Young Gurnam Singh aka Gary). Suvinder Vicky( Sehtab Singh). Pramod Pathak( Chandan Kumar). Geeta Agrawal Sharma( Madam Aulakh). Gurinder Makna( Baljit Singh Rajpuria aka Bill). Hasleen Kaur( Babita Masih). Kavya Thapar( Kimi Aulakh). Sukhwinder Chahal( Mukhtyar Singh). Dakssh Ajit Singh( Lakhwinder Singh aka Laadi). Jaipreet Singh( Shamsher Singh). Danish Sood( Sunny Singh). Manish Gulati( Monty Singh). Eklavey Kashyap( Rocky Ranjha). Elisha Mayor( Sehar Batra). Coral Bhamra( Sweety). Sachin Negi( Heera). Ramandeep Yadav( Saaba). Rehmat Rattan( Keerat Aulakh). Neha Pawar( Young Madam Aulakh). Yuvraj Gadhavi( Hirak Joshi). Kul Sidhu( Nimrat Kaur). Narinder Nina( Swaroop Singh). Swaran Singh( Dilbag Singh). Ajay Bhardwaj( Darbara Singh Aulakh). Navneet Kaur( Bobby Rani). Kp Singh( Jaggi Pardan). Varun Narang( SSP Kamlesh Arora)

Language Punjabi.

Producers Sanjana Chopra. Mahammad Sabir Shaikh. Panchali Chakraverty. Balwinder Singh Janjua.

Production Movie Tunnel Productions.

 

Number of Seasons 1

Number of Episodes 8

Status OnGoing (2022–)
